{"tid":2143634,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［討論］武肺對抗爭利多於弊","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T17:14:05.000Z","uid":106072,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f20cfa89affeaab96b079834619baf50775785","tid":2143634,"uid":106072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:07:39.000Z","msg":"武肺簡直係全球生化武器，影響全球政經社國際關係。<br />\n<br />\n而佢咁岩係區議會選舉勝出為某些人帶來假希望日，抗爭膠著既情況下出現，迫使正苦藉題發揮，推出599G、立法會選舉延遲等加快攬炒速度；另一方面全球開始圍剿強国。<br />\n<br />\n加埋個「健康碼」同DNA測試，GPS同人面識別系統加乘，圍捕無難度，教育營加社會迅級制度指日可待。<br />\n<br />\n如果以攬炒為其中目標，<br />\n武肺係咪利多於弊<br />\n<br />\n令中共顯出真面目，讓叫不醒既人睇清楚現實，讓世界更關注香港。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？<br />\n利多：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n弊多：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcea987aeb34e7d0c7cee8886af4be11785f950","tid":2143634,"uid":106072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa48a7258ab2f879b5ee939e7665cd272fb5e1f7","tid":2143634,"uid":106072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06d0770e29366b74b6fc43c01244d7fe9705f48e","tid":2143634,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情對香港民主運動弊大於利？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2145747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2145747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有類似嘅po喇"},{"pid":"e09498752f43e78f6ba88044915bdf58aad2b4bd","tid":2143634,"uid":106072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06d0770e29366b74b6fc43c01244d7fe9705f48e","tid":2143634,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情對香港民主運動弊大於利？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2145747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2145747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有類似嘅po喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"